attributes.name: Vape Cartridge-Ekto Cooler .5g
attributes.body:
Strain: Hybrid

Fragrance: Orange, lemon, lemongrass

Effects: Uplifting, euphoric

Ekto Kooler is a blast from the past, sent to the future to haunt your taste
buds. Layers of citrus ooze from this flavor, while light pineapple and
fruit notes add depth. It’ll scare you into a good mood.

attributes.name: Vape Cartridge-Wedding Cake .5g
attributes.body:
Strain: Hybrid

Fragrance: Cherry Pie and Girl Scout Cookies blend to form a tasty flavor with lemon and mango highlights
along with creamy lavender notes. A complex variety; the exhale holds
the citrus cream flavor.

Effects: Great for unwinding at the end of the day or just removing the discomfort of the day. Great for lifting your spirits.
